
	genesis: nequi app like simulation (first project)

ABOUT
	Originally this project was called DVSC which stands for the name
	of some people i used to admire back in the time (2020). The project
	simulates a bank app (inspired by Nequi) and it is a CRUD application
	pretty much. It uses SQL and Python3

RUN
	This project cannot longer be executed since it depends on a database
	(which i lost). It could be created but nobody is gonna do that and i
	forgot most of the code

